  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it took us-- they gave us four weeks, the Germans, to get there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But it took us much, much longer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And when we were close to the border already, we were told if this is passed, then--then-- then that's a tragedy, that they are going to kill those who-- there were all kind of-- all kind of rumors, you know.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But people, in that time in Poland, they were dying for hunger.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You could see people on the street, here and there, blown up, blown up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They died just from hunger.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But still, [INAUDIBLE] I remember I had a watch, which I got a present.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was a very big thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We got a lot of things for that watch.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we sold whatever we had-- little things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I really-- I don't know how we managed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But we stood in [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Stryi, ?] which is a bigger town, near the border, where we stood for about a couple of weeks, because our paper was over, you see-- expired.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So that's a long and sad story.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
